From 0000000000000000000000000000000000000006 Mon Sep 17 00:00:00 2001
From: ESP32-S3 Web Simulator contributors <noreply@example.com>
Date: Sun, 19 Jul 2026 12:00:00 +0800
Subject: [PATCH 6/6] esp32s3: model StickS3 buttons, BMI270, and M5PM1

Add active-low GPIO button injection plus deterministic I2C models for
the StickS3 BMI270 IMU and M5PM1 power-management controller. Expose
runtime sensor and power state through private QOM properties.
